Description: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character.  Reduces the endurance cost of a power by {Boost.Attrib.Endurance.Scale}% and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.Recharge.Scale}%.  This enhancement can only be slotted by Controllers and may be slotted into most control powers and requires the user to be level 50.
DisplayName: Superior Attuned Superior Will of the Controller C
SubName: Set: Superior Will of the Controller
